Bulding bsod-client:
----------------------------------
----------------------------------

Linux:
----------------------------------

Install:
 * libsdl1.2-dev
 * libsdl-net1.2-dev
 * libdevil-dev
 * zlib1g-dev
 * libpng-dev
 * libconfig

Build bsod-client:
 * make

Configure bsod-client:
 * vi bsod.conf

Run:
 * ./bsod_client


Windows
----------------------------------

Configure bsod-client:
 * edit bsod.conf

Run:
 * bsod.exe
